  <h1>Plant Security and Tracking</h1>
  <p>Plant and Machinery security and tracking devices give full protection from theft or unauthorised use, however these devices are manufactured with the extreme environment a Plant Machine is subjected to for added reliability.</p>
  <p>Immobilisation is taken care of via a contactless transponder or remotely via Text. Tracking systems for machines can be used for stolen vehicle, fleet management requirements or both integrated into one system.</p>
  <p>"Geo fences" can be added around the machine so if it leaves an area you pre set via the tracking system web site you will be alerted via text or email, this gives you an early warning if it has been stolen or is just being used when it shouldn't be.</p>
